==== 关于主演 ====

由于在《水晶头骨王国》中引入了马特·威廉姆斯（Mutt Williams）（[[希安·拉博夫|希安·拉博夫]]），有人猜测，拉博夫将替代哈里森·福特，接手这一电影系列。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.vanityfair.com/culture/features/2008/02/indy_update200802 | title=My Indiana Jones Crackpot Theory | trans-title=我的印第安纳·琼斯幻想理论 | accessdate=2008-01-17 | date=2008-01-04 | last=Windolf | first=Jim | work=[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]] | language=en | archive-date=2008-01-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080116145137/http://www.vanityfair.com/culture/features/2008/02/indy_update200802 | dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[IGN|IGN]]的一次采访中，“斯皮尔伯格表明，拉博夫需要参与多部[[变形金刚电影系列|变形金刚电影]]，之后他才能抽身，接过印第安纳·琼斯的毡帽和皮鞭。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/826/826026p1.html | title=Indy IV Winding Down | trans-title=夺宝奇兵IV正在放松一下 | accessdate=2008-01-17 | date=2007-10-09 | last=Gilchrist | first=Todd | work=IGN | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012105639/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/826/826026p1.html | archivedate=2007-10-12 | language=en | dead-url=yes }}</ref>而演员自己说：“轮到我了？开玩笑呢？我不认为会这样，这是谣言。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=41086 | title=LaBeouf on Indy 4, Transformers 2 & Y: The Last Man | trans-title=夺宝奇兵4、变形金刚2和Y：最后一个男人中的拉博夫 | accessdate=2008-01-19 | date=2008-01-19 | last=Newgen | first=Heather | work=ComingSoon.net | language=en | archive-date=2008-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080120043625/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=41086 | dead-url=no }}</ref>哈里森·福特说，第五部影片他还会回来，如果不需要再等二十年的话。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-04-16-harrison-ford_N.htm | title=Harrison Ford is a portrait of rugged individualism | trans-title=哈里森·福特粗犷的个人主义的标杆 | accessdate=2008-04-18 | date=2008-04-16 | last=Breznican | first=Anthony | work=[[今日美国|今日美国]] | language=en | archive-date=2008-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080417074817/http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-04-16-harrison-ford_N.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>而斯皮尔伯格则回应说，“除非你们（观众）更想这样”，才会这样。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7406990.stm | title=Spielberg eyes more Indiana films | trans-title=斯皮尔伯格筹划更多的夺宝奇兵电影 | date=2008-05-18 | work=[[BBC新闻网|BBC新闻网]] | accessdate=2008-05-18 | language=en | archive-date=2008-05-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080529024925/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7406990.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>在《时代周刊》的一次采访中，当被问及在下部影片中是否将毡帽传给拉博夫时，哈里森·福特说：“你说什么？它是我的。我要演下一部夺宝奇兵，乔治·卢卡斯现在正在琢磨一个想法。希安可以有他自己的帽子，那顶帽子是我挣来的。”<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1953711-2,00.html | title=10 Questions for Movie Star Harrison Ford | trans-title=对影星哈里森·福特的10个问题 | last=Lipsky | first=Jeff | date=2010-01-25 | work=[[时代周刊|时代周刊]] | accessdate=2016-03-15 | language=en | archive-date=2013-05-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522135032/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1953711-2,00.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

在[[2008年戛纳电影节|2008年戛纳电影节]]上，卢卡斯进一步说明，将会有第五部影片。他还透露了一个想法：“下一次让希安·拉博夫演主角，让哈里森·福特回来，就像[[肖恩·康纳利|肖恩·康纳利]]在前一部影片中那样。”当时拍摄《圣战奇兵》时，肖恩·康纳利只有58岁。卢卡斯也说年龄不是问题，哈里森·福特“已经65岁了，但在这部影片中，一切都是他自己做的。变老是肯定的，但他并不像是个老人。他仍然敏捷得难以置信；他看起来甚至比20年前做得更好，如果你问我的话。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,356282,00.html | title=Lucas: 'Indy 5' a Possibility | trans-title=卢卡斯：《夺宝奇兵5》的可能性 | accessdate=2008-05-16 | date=2008-05-16 | last=Friedman | first=Roger | work=[[福克斯新闻|福克斯新闻]] | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080519112250/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,356282,00.html | archive-date=2008-05-19 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>2008年8月，卢卡斯在研究可能用到的道具，并说斯皮尔伯格对第五部影片持开放态度。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/index.php?category=0&id=58310&type=0 | title=Lucas: Indy V Research In Works | trans-title=卢卡斯：正在研究夺宝奇兵V | accessdate=2008-08-05 | date=2008-08-05 | last=Lee | first=Patrick | work=Sci Fi Wire | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080805034337/http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/index.php?category=0 | archivedate=2008-08-05 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>他还改变了自己“继续这一系列并分拆”的想法，开玩笑说“印第安纳·琼斯就是印第安纳·琼斯。哈里森·福特就是印第安纳·琼斯。如果是马特·威廉姆斯，那就是《马特·威廉姆斯与搜寻[[猫王|猫王]]》什么的。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/08/05/exclusive-indiana-jones-5-wont-center-on-shia-labeouf-george-lucas-insists/ | title='Indiana Jones 5' Won't Center on Shia LaBeouf, Insists George Lucas | trans-title=乔治·卢卡斯坚持，《夺宝奇兵5》不会以希安·拉博夫为中心 | accessdate=2008-08-05 | date=2008-08-05 | last=Adler | first=Shawn | work=[[MTV|MTV]]电影博客 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828035243/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/08/05/exclusive-indiana-jones-5-wont-center-on-shia-labeouf-george-lucas-insists/ | archivedate=2008-08-28 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>两个月之后，哈里森·福特说，如果第五部影片是一部像《[[星球大战：克隆人之战_(电影)|克隆人之战]]》那样的动画电影，他就不演了，因为“我不希望看到我们制作的电影及其制作方式有任何方面的缺失。”他还称，卢卡斯对第五部影片的想法“很疯狂，但是很棒”。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2008/10/harrison-ford-s.html | title=Harrison Ford says George Lucas in 'think mode' on another 'Indiana Jones' film | trans-title=哈里森·福特说，乔治·卢卡斯正为另一部《夺宝奇兵》电影处于“思考模式” | accessdate=2008-10-05 | date=2008-10-03 | last=Boucher | first=Geoff | work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]] | language=en | archive-date=2008-10-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081004140553/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2008/10/harrison-ford-s.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

当被问及与马里昂·瑞文伍德结婚并有了一个儿子，在第五部影片中会如何影响角色，哈里森·福特仅回答说：“他见过一些东西，而这些东西又是仅有的能证明他见过的证据。这很有趣。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/11/19/exclusive-harrison-ford-talks-fifth-indiana-jones-film/ | title=Harrison Ford Talks Fifth Indiana Jones Film | trans-title=哈里森·福特谈论第五部夺宝奇兵电影 | accessdate=2008-11-19 | date=2008-11-19 | last=Horowitz | first=Josh | work=[[MTV|MTV]]电影博客 | language=en | archive-date=2008-12-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081224154028/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/11/19/exclusive-harrison-ford-talks-fifth-indiana-jones-film/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>在2010年1月，哈里森·福特说：“我想，增进对角色的理解会很有趣，因为我们对整个系列始终雄心勃勃。我认为，加深他和他儿子之间的关系，并在这个关系的基础上演绎，将会很有趣……它充满了机会。这个系列也充满了机会。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1629378/story.jhtml | title=Harrison Ford Says Next Indiana Jones Movie Is 'Full Of Opportunity' | trans-title=哈里森·福特说下一部夺宝奇兵电影“充满了机会” | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2010-01-08 | last=Carroll | first=Larry | work=MTV新闻 | language=en | archive-date=2010-03-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100318045125/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1629378/story.jhtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==== 关于《夺宝奇兵5》 ====

从2009年到2010年都在继续讨论《夺宝奇兵5》的可行性。2009年6月有报道推测，下一部将于2011年开拍，其情节涉及[[百慕大三角|百慕大三角]]。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://thefilmstage.com/2010/06/07/final-indiana-jones-film-involves-the-bermuda-triangle-to-shoot-next-year/ | title=Final Indiana Jones Film Involves The Bermuda Triangle, To Shoot Next Year | trans-title=最后一部夺宝奇兵影片涉及到，明年开拍 | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2010-06-07 | work=The Film Stage | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100825224349/http://thefilmstage.com/2010/06/07/final-indiana-jones-film-involves-the-bermuda-triangle-to-shoot-next-year/ | archivedate=2010-08-25 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>但后来法兰克·马歇尔在其Twitter上说，这些传言是“完全错误的”。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://twitter.com/LeDoctor/status/15795474772 | title=Frank Marshall: The rumor about INDY 5 is... | trans-title=法兰克·马歇尔：关于夺宝奇兵5的传言是…… | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2010-06-09 | last=Marshall | first=Frank | author-link=法兰克·马歇尔 | work=[[Twitter|Twitter]] | quote=The rumor about INDY 5 is completely false. Nothing has changed, we are not shooting next year and still in the research phase...[关于夺宝奇兵5的传言是完全错误的。什么都没变，我们不会在明年开拍，仍在研究阶段……] | language=en | archive-date=2016-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410011734/https://twitter.com/LeDoctor/status/15795474772 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年6月，拉博夫向[[BBC|BBC]]记者{{link-en|利佐·姆津巴|Lizo Mzimba}}确认：“斯蒂芬（斯皮尔伯格）只是说，他构思了它（第五部影片）的故事，我想他们正在加速。”<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/8102103.stm | title=Shia LaBeouf talks Transformers | trans-title=希安·拉博夫谈论变形金刚 | date=2009-06-15 | work=[[BBC新闻网|BBC新闻网]] | accessdate=2009-06-16 | language=en | archive-date=2017-08-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826082058/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/8102103.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>卢卡斯说他从2009年12月开始忙于这部影片。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.thearnoldfans.com/news/1576.htm | title=TAFs on the Red Carpet for Cal Hall of Fame 2009! Interviews with Lucas, Burnett and Joe Weider! | trans-title=施瓦辛格迷们在传说2009的Cal Hall的红毯上！对卢卡斯、伯内特和乔·魏德的访谈！ | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2009-12-03 | last=Jennings | first=Randy | work=The Arnold Fans | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309055043/http://www.thearnoldfans.com/news/1576.htm | archivedate=2012-03-09 | quote=The next Indy film? Yes, we're working on it. It's in development. That's all I can say right now.[下一部夺宝奇兵电影？是的，我们正忙这呢。它正在开发中。我现在只能说这么多。] | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年11月，哈里森·福特说，他和斯皮尔伯格在等待卢卡斯向他们讲述他的想法。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1651767/20101108/story.jhtml | title=Harrison Ford Is 'Looking Forward' To 'Indiana Jones 5' | trans-title=哈里森·福特正在“展望”《夺宝奇兵5》 | accessdate=2016-03-05 | date=2010-11-08 | last=Ditzian | first=Eric | work=MTV新闻 | language=en | archive-date=2010-12-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213075214/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1651767/20101108/story.jhtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年3月，Deadbolt网站采访凯伦·阿兰，并询问了她关于第五部影片的情况。“我知道的是，他们有了一个他们喜欢的故事，”阿兰说，“这是一个巨大的进步。我是大概半年前听说的，他们有了一个喜欢的故事，并且他们正在忙于这件事。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.thedeadbolt.com/news/110494/karen_allen_indiana_jones_5.php | title=Karen Allen Talks Indiana Jones 5 | trans-title=Karen Allen Talks Indiana Jones 5 | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2011-03-25 | last=Seeton | first=Reg | work=The Dead Bolt | quote=What I know is that there's a story that they like, which is a huge step forward.[我知道的是，有一个他们喜欢的故事，这是一个巨大的进步。] | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309233209/http://www.thedeadbolt.com/news/110494/karen_allen_indiana_jones_5.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年7月，[[法兰克·马歇尔|法兰克·马歇尔]]表示，该片不大可能在近期宣布，他说：“我不敢肯定它不会发生，但它还没有步入正轨……这个项目得先有编剧才行。现在夺宝奇兵还没有编剧。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2012/07/indiana-jones-5-may-not-happen-but-jurassic-park-4-still-might | title=Frank Marshall talks Indy 5 and Jurassic Park 4 | trans-title=法兰克·马歇尔谈论夺宝奇兵5和侏罗纪公园4 | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2012-07-31 | work=Complex.com | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171151/http://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2012/07/indiana-jones-5-may-not-happen-but-jurassic-park-4-still-might | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年10月，[[迪斯尼公司|迪斯尼公司]]收购了[[卢卡斯影业|卢卡斯影业]]，从而获得了《夺宝奇兵》[[知识产权|知识产权]]的所有权。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-rt-disney-george-lucasmt1thewrap62801-20121030,0,3587016.story | title=Disney to Buy Lucasfilm for $4.05B, Plans New 'Star Wars' Films | trans-title=迪斯尼40.5亿美元购入卢卡斯影业，筹划新的《星球大战》影片 | accessdate=2012-11-01 | date=2012-10-30 | last=Shaw | first=Lucas | work=[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]] | language=en | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101084832/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-rt-disney-george-lucasmt1thewrap62801-20121030,0,3587016.story | archivedate=2012-11-01 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/oct/31/business/la-fi-ct-disney-lucasfilm-20121101 | title=Disney would acquire a visual effects firm with Lucasfilm deal | trans-title=迪斯尼将与卢卡斯影业交易，收购一个视觉效果公司 | date=2012-10-31 | work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]] | accessdate=2012-11-04 | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234709/http://articles.latimes.com/2012/oct/31/business/la-fi-ct-disney-lucasfilm-20121101 | dead-url=no }}</ref>但是，[[派拉蒙影业|派拉蒙影业]]仍然拥有该电影系列的[[电影发行|发行权]]。<ref name="Eric Eisenberg">{{Cite web | url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Indiana-Jones-Return-Disney-33838.html | title=Will Indiana Jones Return At Disney? | trans-title=在迪斯尼，印第安纳·琼斯还会回来么？ | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2012-10-30 | last=Eisenberg | first=Eric | work=Cinema Blend | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318035958/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Indiana-Jones-Return-Disney-33838.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/11/01/disney-lucasfilm-deal-indiana-jones/ | title=What about Indy? The Disney/Lucasfilm deal and the future of 'Indiana Jones' | trans-title=印第怎么样了？迪斯尼/卢卡斯影业的交易与《夺宝奇兵》的未来》 | accessdate=2013-02-09 | date=2012-11-01 | last=Vary | first=Adam | work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]] | language=en | archive-date=2013-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126184945/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/11/01/disney-lucasfilm-deal-indiana-jones/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年12月6日，[[迪斯尼集团|迪斯尼集团]]购买了剩下的、对未来《夺宝奇兵》影片的发行权和销售权，而派拉蒙将保留前四部影片的发行权，并将参与任何后续影片的“分红”。<ref name="VarDisney">{{Cite web | url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/disney-acquires-indiana-jones-rights-from-paramount-1200927216/ | title=Disney Acquires Rights to Future 'Indiana Jones' Movies | trans-title=迪斯尼收购未来《夺宝奇兵》影片的权利 | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2013-12-06 | last=Kroll | first=Justin | work=[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]] | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319134349/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/disney-acquires-indiana-jones-rights-from-paramount-1200927216/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="LATDisney">{{Cite web | url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-disney-acquires-future-indiana-jones-rights-paramount-20131206,0,4071440.story#axzz2mom6ecrD | title=Disney acquires control of future 'Indiana Jones' movies | trans-title=迪斯尼收购对未来《夺宝奇兵》影片的控制权 | accessdate=2013-12-07 | date=2013-12-06 | last=Faughnder | first=Ryan | work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]] | language=en | archive-date=2013-12-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207185042/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-disney-acquires-future-indiana-jones-rights-paramount-20131206,0,4071440.story#axzz2mom6ecrD | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="THRDisney">{{Cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-takes-control-indiana-jones-663704 | title=Disney Takes Control of 'Indiana Jones' Franchise for Future Films | trans-title=迪斯尼取得对《夺宝奇兵》系列的未来影片的控制权 | accessdate=2013-12-07 | date=2013-12-06 | last=Ford | first=Rebecca | work=[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]] | language=en | archive-date=2013-12-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207023629/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-takes-control-indiana-jones-663704 | dead-url=no }}</ref>尽管该交易并未宣布有新的影片，但是迪斯尼CEO[[罗伯特·艾格|罗伯特·艾格]]已经表示有兴趣通过迪斯尼各部门的合作将该系列变现。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/read-bob-igers-letter-to-disney-staffers-about-the-lucasfilm-acquisition-6010/ | title=READ: Disney chief Bob Iger's internal memo to staff: 'Lucasfilm fits perfectly with Disney's strategic priorities' | trans-title=读：迪斯尼CEO罗伯特·艾格对员工的内部备忘录：“卢卡斯影业完全适合迪斯尼的战略优先级” | accessdate=2013-11-13 | date=2012-10-30 | last=Oldham | first=Stuart | work=综艺 | language=en | archive-date=2013-12-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203064543/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/read-bob-igers-letter-to-disney-staffers-about-the-lucasfilm-acquisition-6010/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>集团主席{{link-en|艾伦·霍恩|Alan Horn}}说，第五部《夺宝奇兵》影片至少需要准备两三年。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://variety.com/2013/biz/news/dont-expect-the-next-indiana-jones-for-at-least-two-to-three-years-1200952951/ | title=Don't Expect a New Indiana Jones Movie for at Least Two to Three Years | trans-title=至少两三年不要期望新的夺宝奇兵影片 | last=Graser | first=Marc | date=2013-12-13 | work=综艺 | accessdate=2013-12-14 | language=en | archive-date=2014-03-29 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20140329171050/http://variety.com/2013/biz/news/dont-expect-the-next-indiana-jones-for-at-least-two-to-three-years-1200952951/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2015年5月《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》的一次采访中，凯瑟琳·肯尼迪确认了第五部影片的计划，她说另一部影片“有一天将会在公司内制作。但是会在什么时候，我不是很确定。我们还没有开始为它写脚本，但我们正在讨论。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/05/indiana-jones-sequel-confirmed | title=Lucasfilm President Finally Confirms Indiana Jones Sequel Is on the Horizon | trans-title=卢卡斯影业总裁终于确认夺宝奇兵续集即将来临 | accessdate=2016-03-15 | work=[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]] | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314215810/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/05/indiana-jones-sequel-confirmed | dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年10月，斯皮尔伯格告诉{{link-en|雅虎！电影|Yahoo! Movies}}，哈里森·福特将有可能在第五部《夺宝奇兵》影片中再次饰演他的角色。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.yahoo.com/movies/tom-hanks-and-steven-spielberg-on-indiana-jones-173307833.html | title=Tom Hanks and Steven Spielberg on 'Indiana Jones 5' and Saving 'Forrest Gump' | trans-title=汤姆·汉克斯和斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格谈《夺宝奇兵5》和拯救《阿甘正传》 | accessdate=2015-10-12 | date=2015-10-09 | last=Watkins | first=Gwynne | work={{link-en|雅虎！电影|Yahoo! Movies}} | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012222648/https://www.yahoo.com/movies/tom-hanks-and-steven-spielberg-on-indiana-jones-173307833.html | archivedate=2015-10-12 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年3月15日，迪斯尼集团宣布，第五部影片将在2019年7月19日上映。主演依然是哈里森·福特，斯皮尔伯格将担任导演，由大卫·柯普编剧，制片为凯瑟琳·肯尼迪和法兰克·马歇尔。乔治·卢卡斯起初不打算参与这部电影。<ref name="Deadline Fifth Film">{{Cite web | url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/steven-spielberg-harrison-ford-team-up-for-indiana-jones-5-disney-sets-july-2019-release-1201720725/ | title=Steven Spielberg & Harrison Ford Team Up For 'Indiana Jones 5', Disney Sets July 2019 Release | trans-title=斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格和哈里森·福特合作《夺宝奇兵5》，迪斯尼打算2019年7月上映 | accessdate=2016-03-15 | date=2016-03-15 | last=D'Alessandro | first=Anthony | publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | language=en | archive-date=2016-06-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623145252/http://deadline.com/2016/03/steven-spielberg-harrison-ford-team-up-for-indiana-jones-5-disney-sets-july-2019-release-1201720725/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/indiana-jones-5-enlists-crystal-876684 | title=Steven Spielberg Enlists a Familiar Writer for 'Indiana Jones 5' (Exclusive) | trans-title=斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格找熟悉的编剧来写《夺宝奇兵5》（独家） | accessdate=2016-03-18 | date=2016-03-18 | last=Kit | first=Borys | work=[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]] | archive-date=2016-03-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320154658/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/indiana-jones-5-enlists-crystal-876684 | dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，在迪士尼《[[圆梦巨人_(2016年电影)|圆梦巨人]]》的一次新闻发布会上，斯皮尔伯格确认，卢卡斯将再次作为执行制片，他说：“我绝不能让一部《夺宝奇兵》缺了乔治·卢卡斯。那太扯淡了。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.slashfilm.com/indiana-jones-5-george-lucas/ | title=Indiana Jones 5: George Lucas to Executive Produce | trans-title=夺宝奇兵5：乔治·卢卡斯作执行制片 | accessdate=2016-07-03 | date=2016-06-22 | language=en | archive-date=2016-06-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625112323/http://www.slashfilm.com/indiana-jones-5-george-lucas/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>法兰克·马歇尔表示，该片将延续《水晶头骨王国》的故事。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/frank-marshall-indiana-jones-harrison-ford-cinemacon-1201750527/ | title=Frank Marshall: Harrison Ford Is One and Only 'Indiana Jones,' 'Not Going to Do the Bond Thing' | trans-title=法兰克·马歇尔：哈里森·福特是唯一的“印第安纳·琼斯”，“不会像邦德那样” | last=Rainey | first=James | date=2016-04-11 | work=[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]] | accessdate=2016-04-12 | language=en | archive-date=2016-04-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412115821/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/frank-marshall-indiana-jones-harrison-ford-cinemacon-1201750527/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年6月9日，斯皮尔伯格确认，[[约翰·威廉姆斯|约翰·威廉姆斯]]将再次加盟。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.slashfilm.com/star-wars-episode-viii-score/ | title=John Williams Will Compose Indiana Jones 5 and Star Wars Episode VIII Score | trans-title=约翰·威廉姆斯将加盟夺宝奇兵5和星球大战VIII | accessdate=2016-06-10 | date=2016-06-10 | language=en | archive-date=2016-06-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611131950/http://www.slashfilm.com/star-wars-episode-viii-score/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年4月25日，《星球大战》官方网站将该片的上映日期更新到了2020年7月10日。<ref name="StarWars.com" />2017年9月4日，大卫·柯普透漏，由[[希安·拉博夫|希安·拉博夫]]扮演的马特·威廉姆斯的角色将不会再次出现。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/09/04/indiana-jones-5-shia-labeouf-not-returning/ | title=Indiana Jones 5 won't feature Shia LaBeouf's character | trans-title=夺宝奇兵5将不使用希安·拉博夫的角色 | accessdate=2017-09-04 | date=2017-09-04 | last=Nolfi | first=Joey | publisher=[[时代公司|时代公司]] | language=en | archive-date=2017-09-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904182823/http://ew.com/movies/2017/09/04/indiana-jones-5-shia-labeouf-not-returning/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

斯皮尔伯格和[[迪斯尼|迪斯尼]]的[[罗伯特·艾格|罗伯特·艾格]]都谈论了第五部影片。斯皮尔伯格表示，印第安纳·琼斯不会消失。然而，艾格说，这个有哈里森·福特的系列，其未来是未知的，但是第五部影片“不会是最后一部。”<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/884789-shia-labeoufs-mutt-williams-is-not-in-indiana-jones-5#/slide/1 | title=Shia LaBeouf’s Mutt Williams is Not in Indiana Jones 5 | trans-title=希安·拉博夫的马特·威廉姆斯不在夺宝奇兵5里 | accessdate=2017-09-04 | date=2017-09-04 | work=ComingSoon.net | language=en | archive-date=2017-09-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904171048/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/884789-shia-labeoufs-mutt-williams-is-not-in-indiana-jones-5#/slide/1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

