nguage=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121004930/http://www.action-figure.com/index.php?name=News&file=article&sid=22701 | archive-date=2016-01-21 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>配合第四部影片的上映，[[乐高|乐高]]发布了八个套装，它们基于《-{zh-cn:夺宝奇兵; zh-hk:奪寶奇兵; zh-tw:法櫃奇兵;}-》、《圣战奇兵》和《水晶头骨王国》。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://indianajones.lego.com/en-us/Products/IndianaJones/7620.aspx | title=Indiana Jones – Products | trans-title=夺宝奇兵–产品 | accessdate=2008-02-17 | publisher=[[乐高|乐高]] | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080210000314/http://indianajones.lego.com/en-us/Products/IndianaJones/7620.aspx | archive-date=2008-02-10 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=https://gizmodo.com/350473/new-indy-movie-lego-sets-offer-exclusive-peek-into-crystal-skull | title=New Indy Movie LEGO Sets Offer Exclusive Peek Into Crystal Skull | trans-title=新夺宝奇兵电影乐高套装独家透露水晶头骨 | publisher=[[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] | accessdate=2008-02-17 | language=en | archive-date=2008-02-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080213105232/http://gizmodo.com/350473/new-indy-movie-lego-sets-offer-exclusive-peek-into-crystal-skull | dead-url=no }}</ref>

